{"tid":1278541,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[489入] 指原莉乃疑整容鼻變尖似巫婆","createTime":"2019-07-02T13:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T09:14:05.000Z","uid":74065,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"34317defff1ea2d5036cfd380eb6d5a5163376c0","tid":1278541,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190702/photo/bkn-20190702123234797-0702_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190702132556\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190702%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190702123234797-0702_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190702132556&h=871ae915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指原莉乃現身最近一集《有吉反省會》，樣子明顯跟以前有分別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190702/photo/bkn-20190702123234797-0702_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190702132556\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190702%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190702123234797-0702_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190702132556&h=df04403d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似整容前後對比，左排圖片是整容前，鼻型較圓，右排圖片鼻子變尖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190702/photo/bkn-20190702123234797-0702_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190702132556\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190702%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190702123234797-0702_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190702132556&h=5e21251a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雙眼皮和鼻子明顯做過手腳。<br />\n<br />\n日本女團HKT48前一姐指原莉乃，再次被懷疑整容。有網友發現她日前現身綜藝節目《有吉反省會》，樣子明顯跟以前有分別，差點認不出是她。<br />\n<br />\n網友指出雙眼皮比以前深了很多，鼻頭估計打了玻尿酸，鼻形愈來愈尖，有點似巫婆，網友形容她愈來愈似韓國人的整容樣版。指原已非第一次被指疑似整容，她亦極力否認，但網友將她昔日與近日照片對比，完全是兩個人樣，昔日鼻形較圓，現在變尖，她否認只會令人覺得是講大話。"},{"pid":"a265e950ee31f2376c9160e9f10395afc46091dc","tid":1278541,"uid":242537,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"整完都咁撚醜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f